concerning the ra&s;tle was immediately
forgotten.</P>
<P>A &s;hort con&s;ultation followed, in which both
&s;poke with &s;o much energy, as not only to overpower
<PB N="112" REF="112">
the remon&s;trances of Mi&s;s Margland for their depar|ture,
