<P><PB N="151" REF="151">
The a&s;toni&s;hed Eugenia, though at fir&s;t all emo|tion,
was completely recovered by this action. His
kneeling and his &startq;O madam!&endq; had every chance
to affect her; but his ki&s;&s;ing her hand &s;he thought a
