irreparable as it was irrem$diable&punc;</P>
<P>Bellamy, who, from her $ett$r, had augured
nothing of hardne&s;s of heart, t$nderly $$lie$$ed her
forgivene&s;s; but &s;he made him no an&s;wer: &s;ilent
